text.tspan: Prevalence of eating disorders in males vs. females, 2019
Share of population suffering from an eating disorder, in males versus females. Data includes only eating disorders
clinically defined as anorexia or bulimia nervosa. Figures attempt to provide a true estimate (going beyond
reported diagnosis) of eating disorder prevalence based on medical, epidemiological data, surveys and
Data source: IHME, Global Burden of Disease (2019)
